2011－2012年，'''[[約旦|約旦]]'''發生一系列的示威抗議活動，起因為[[失業|失業]]問題、[[通貨膨脹|通貨膨脹]]<ref name="nytimesDismissesCabinet">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/02/02/world/middleeast/02jordan.html|title=Jordan's King Dismisses Cabinet as Tremors Spread Through Region|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|first1=Ranya|last1=Kadri|first2=Ethan|last2=Bronner|date=1 February 2011|access-date=2018-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106132437/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/02/02/world/middleeast/02jordan.html|archive-date=2018-11-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[政治腐敗|政治腐敗]]等<ref>[http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2011/Dec-02/155857-protesters-demand-saving-jordan-from-corruption.ashx "Protesters demand 'saving' Jordan from corruption"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2011/Dec-02/155857-protesters-demand-saving-jordan-from-corruption.ashx |date=20181106132638 }}. ''The Daily Star'' (Lebanon), (2 December 2011).</ref>。示威群眾要求實行真正的[[君主立憲|君主立憲]]<ref name="google1"/>，並進行{{link-en|選制改革|electoral reform}}<ref>[https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/jordan/9590706/Thousands-rally-to-demand-reform-in-Jordan.html "Thousands rally to demand reform in Jordan"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/jordan/9590706/Thousands-rally-to-demand-reform-in-Jordan.html |date=20181106132453 }}. ''The Daily Telegraph'', (5 October 2012).</ref>。長期的示威抗議導致[[約旦國王|約旦國王]][[阿卜杜拉二世|阿卜杜拉二世]]在18個月內三度撤換內閣[[約旦首相|首相]]，並於2012年解散國會，提前於隔年舉行選舉。

[[2011年埃及革命|2011年埃及革命]]和發生於[[突尼西亞|突尼西亞]]的[[茉莉花革命|茉莉花革命]]也帶來了此區域政治改革的呼聲。這次示威和發生在[[中東|中東]]、[[北非|北非]]等地的其他示威同為[[阿拉伯之春|阿拉伯之春]]的一部分。

